---

<Layout title="Sobre | Lucas Ramos">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-8">

    <!-- Voltar -->
    <a href="/" class="text-neonCyan font-mono text-xs hover:underline mb-10 inline-flex items-center gap-1 pt-only">&larr; VOLTAR</a>
    <a href="/" class="text-neonCyan font-mono text-xs hover:underline mb-10 inline-flex items-center gap-1 en-only">&larr; BACK</a>
    <a href="/" class="text-neonCyan font-mono text-xs hover:underline mb-10 inline-flex items-center gap-1 fr-only">&larr; RETOUR</a>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <header class="mb-16 pb-10 border-b border-surfaceHighlight">
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-end sm:justify-between gap-6">
        <div>
          <p class="font-mono text-xs text-neonCyan mb-3 tracking-widest pt-only">ENGENHEIRO DE DADOS & FOTÓGRAFO</p>
          <p class="font-mono text-xs text-neonCyan mb-3 tracking-widest en-only">DATA ENGINEER & PHOTOGRAPHER</p>
          <p class="font-mono text-xs text-neonCyan mb-3 tracking-widest fr-only">INGÉNIEUR DE DONNÉES & PHOTOGRAPHE</p>
          <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight">Lucas<br/><span class="text-neonLime">Ramos</span><span class="text-neonCyan">.</span></h1>
          <p class="text-textMuted mt-3 font-mono text-sm">São José, Santa Catarina, Brasil</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-right sm:pb-1">
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ramoslucas-lr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="font-mono text-xs text-textMuted hover:text-neonCyan transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 sm:justify-end">
            <span>linkedin.com/in/ramoslucas-lr/</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"/></svg>
          </a>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-textMuted">📍 RD Station · Remoto</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bio -->
      <div class="mt-8 text-textMuted leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        <p class="pt-only">Engenheiro de Dados Sênior com experiência em pipelines de alta escala, ETL/ELT, processamento em tempo real e automação de workflows. Proficiente em Python, SQL, Apache Kafka, Airflow e GCP/Azure. Fora do trabalho, capturo o mundo com uma câmera Canon — paisagens, texturas e instantes que a engenharia não consegue calcular.</p>
        <p class="en-only">Senior Data Engineer experienced in high-scale pipelines, ETL/ELT, real-time processing, and workflow automation. Proficient in Python, SQL, Apache Kafka, Airflow, GCP, and Azure. Outside work, I capture the world with a Canon camera — landscapes, textures, and moments that engineering cannot calculate.</p>
        <p class="fr-only">Ingénieur de Données Senior expérimenté en pipelines haute échelle, ETL/ELT, traitement en temps réel et automatisation de workflows. Maîtrise de Python, SQL, Apache Kafka, Airflow, GCP et Azure. En dehors du travail, je capture le monde avec un appareil photo Canon — paysages, textures et instants que l'ingénierie ne sait pas calculer.</p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Experiência -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest text-neonCyan mb-8 pt-only">// EXPERIÊNCIA</h2>
      <h2 class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest text-neonCyan mb-8 en-only">// EXPERIENCE</h2>
      <h2 class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest text-neonCyan mb-8 fr-only">// EXPÉRIENCE</h2>

      <div class="relative">
        <!-- linha vertical -->
        <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-surfaceHighlight ml-[7px] hidden sm:block"></div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
          {experiences.map((exp) => (
            <div class="sm:pl-8 relative group">
              <!-- dot -->
              <div class={`hidden sm:block absolute left-0 top-1 w-4 h-4 rounded-full border-2 ${exp.color === 'cyan' ? 'border-neonCyan bg-base group-hover:bg-neonCyan' : 'border-neonLime bg-base group-hover:bg-neonLime'} transition-colors`}></div>

              <div class="bg-surface border border-surfaceHighlight rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-opacity-60 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg">
                <div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-3 mb-4">
                  <div>
                    <span class={`font-mono text-xs tracking-wider ${exp.color === 'cyan' ? 'text-neonCyan' : 'text-neonLime'}`}>{exp.company}</span>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mt-0.5 pt-only">{exp.role.pt}</h3>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mt-0.5 en-only">{exp.role.en}</h3>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mt-0.5 fr-only">{exp.role.fr}</h3>
                  </div>
                  <div class="text-right">
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-textMuted pt-only">{exp.period.pt}</p>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-textMuted en-only">{exp.period.en}</p>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-textMuted fr-only">{exp.period.fr}</p>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-textMuted mt-0.5 pt-only">{exp.location.pt}</p>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-textMuted mt-0.5 en-only">{exp.location.en}</p>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-textMuted mt-0.5 fr-only">{exp.location.fr}</p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <ul class="space-y-1.5 mb-4">
                  {exp.bullets.pt.map((b) => (
                    <li class="text-sm text-textMuted pt-only flex gap-2"><span class="text-neonLime mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">›</span><span>{b}</span></li>
                  ))}
                  {exp.bullets.en.map((b) => (
                    <li class="text-sm text-textMuted en-only flex gap-2"><span class="text-neonLime mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">›</span><span>{b}</span></li>
                  ))}
                  {exp.bullets.fr.map((b) => (
                    <li class="text-sm text-textMuted fr-only flex gap-2"><span class="text-neonLime mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">›</span><span>{b}</span></li>
                  ))}
                </ul>

                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
                  {exp.tags.map((tag) => (
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-mono px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-surfaceHighlight text-textMuted">{tag}</span>
                  ))}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Skills -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest text-neonCyan mb-8 pt-only">// COMPETÊNCIAS TÉCNICAS</h2>
      <h2 class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest text-neonCyan mb-8 en-only">// TECHNICAL SKILLS</h2>
      <h2 class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest text-neonCyan mb-8 fr-only">// COMPÉTENCES TECHNIQUES</h2>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {skills.map((skill) => (
          <span class="font-mono text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-neonCyan/10 to-neonLime/10 hover:from-neonCyan/20 hover:to-neonLime/20 text-textMain transition-colors duration-200" style="border-image: linear-gradient(to right, var(--color-accent-1), var(--color-accent-2)) 1">
            {skill}
          </span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Formação & Certificações -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">

      <!-- Formação -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest text-neonCyan mb-6 pt-only">// FORMAÇÃO</h2>
        <h2 class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest text-neonCyan mb-6 en-only">// EDUCATION</h2>
        <h2 class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest text-neonCyan mb-6 fr-only">// FORMATION</h2>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <div class="bg-surface border border-surfaceHighlight rounded-2xl p-5">
            <span class="font-mono text-xs text-neonLime">UFSC</span>
            <p class="font-bold text-sm mt-1 pt-only">Bacharelado em Sistemas de Informação</p>
            <p class="font-bold text-sm mt-1 en-only">B.Sc. in Information Systems</p>
            <p class="font-bold text-sm mt-1 fr-only">Licence en Systèmes d'Information</p>
            <p class="font-mono text-xs text-textMuted mt-1">2025 – 2029</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface border border-surfaceHighlight rounded-2xl p-5">
            <span class="font-mono text-xs text-neonLime">UFSC</span>
            <p class="font-bold text-sm mt-1 pt-only">Engenharia Elétrica (curso interrompido)</p>
            <p class="font-bold text-sm mt-1 en-only">Electrical Engineering (incomplete)</p>
            <p class="font-bold text-sm mt-1 fr-only">Génie Électrique (non terminé)</p>
            <p class="font-mono text-xs text-textMuted mt-1">2016 – …</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface border border-surfaceHighlight rounded-2xl p-5">
            <span class="font-mono text-xs text-neonLime">IFC</span>
            <p class="font-bold text-sm mt-1 pt-only">Técnico em Informática Integrado ao Ensino Médio</p>
            <p class="font-bold text-sm mt-1 en-only">High School with Technical IT Degree</p>
            <p class="font-bold text-sm mt-1 fr-only">Bac Technologique en Informatique</p>
            <p class="font-mono text-xs text-textMuted mt-1">2013 – 2015</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Certificações + Idiomas -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-8">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest text-neonCyan mb-6 pt-only">// CERTIFICAÇÕES</h2>
